'''Guardian''' was an elite rank in the [[Guiteica Militia]], given to the personal [[Bodyguard/Legends|bodyguards]] of militia leaders. Guardian [[Aul Tarrus Vishav]] saved the life of [[m'Yalfor'ac Order]] leader [[Quaal Tavier Catharius]] during a duel against [[Major/Legends|Major]] [[Jael Ganton Farvash]]. Farvash intended to kill Catharius through treacherous means, prompting Vishav to step in and defend his leader.<ref name="AIR">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>

